directory: nvim/lua
summary: Neovim Lua plugin root. Exposes the `steno-ts` plugin to callers via `require("steno-ts")`, providing a steno-aware snippet expander keyed off Plover-emitted sentinel tokens.
children:
  - steno-ts/: The complete plugin implementation — setup entrypoint, token detection, and LSP snippet expansion.
key_invariants:
  - All external callers interact solely through `require("steno-ts").setup(opts)`; no other symbols are part of the public contract.